# Workflow: Bug Fix

---

## 1) Reproduce

- [ ] Confirm the bug exists in the target environment/version.
- [ ] Capture reproduction steps and expected vs actual behaviour.
- [ ] Add logs/screenshots if relevant.

## 2) Diagnose

- [ ] Identify root cause (not just symptoms).
- [ ] Determine blast radius (where else it may occur).

## 3) Fix

- [ ] Implement the smallest safe fix.
- [ ] Add a regression test if practical.

## 4) Validate

- [ ] Format: `{{format_cmd}}`
- [ ] Lint: `{{lint_cmd}}`
- [ ] Test: `{{test_cmd}}`

## 5) PR

- [ ] Include: root cause, fix summary, verification steps.
- [ ] Note risk and rollback.

